observationText: The HCT116 cell line, which has an NF1 mutation, did not express detectable levels of the NF1 protein.
The HCT116 cell line, which has both an NF1 mutation and a KRAS G13D mutation, was insensitive to the drug cetuximab.
The HCT116 cell line was one of three colorectal cancer cell lines found to have both a KRAS G13D mutation and an NF1 mutation.
